import React from "react";
import { Form, FormGroup, Input ,} from "reactstrap";

function AddCourse() {
  return (
    <>
      <Form>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="userId">Course ID</Label>
          <Input
            type="text"
            placeholder="Enter userId Here"
            name="userId"
            id="userId"
          ></Input>
        </FormGroup>

        <FormGroup>
    <Label for="examplePassword">
      Password
    </Label>
    <Input
      id="examplePassword"
      name="password"
      placeholder="password placeholder"
      type="password"
    />
  </FormGroup>

  <FormGroup>
    <Label for="exampleText">
      Text Area
    </Label>
    <Input
      id="exampleText"
      name="text"
      type="textarea"
    />
  </FormGroup>
      </Form>
    </>
  );
}
export default AddCourse;
